## Configuration

Environment variables in `scripts/review.sh`:

| Variable | Default | Description |
|----------|---------|-------------|
| `CODEX_MODEL` | `gpt-5.4` | Codex model for reviews |
| `GEMINI_MODEL` | `gemini-3-flash-preview` | Gemini model for reviews |
| `REVIEW_EFFORT` | `high` | Codex reasoning effort |
| `REVIEW_TIMEOUT` | `600` | Timeout per review in seconds |

Override per-session:
```bash
CODEX_MODEL=gpt-5.4-mini /build "quick task"
```

