## Troubleshooting

| Problem | Solution |
|---------|----------|
| `codex: command not found` | `source ~/.bashrc` or add `~/.npm-global/bin` to PATH |
| `Codex not authenticated` | Run `codex auth` or set `CODEX_API_KEY` |
| `Gemini not authenticated` | Run `gemini` or set `GEMINI_API_KEY` |
| `exhausted your capacity` | Gemini free tier rate limit. Wait a few seconds or use an API key. |
| Review times out | Increase `REVIEW_TIMEOUT` env var. Default is 600s. |
| `reviewer did not produce a parseable verdict` | Model didn't output fenced JSON. Try again — intermittent. |
| `No diff found` | No changes between base ref and HEAD. Make sure you've made changes. |
| State file corrupted | Delete `.claude/local/build-state-<branch>.json` and restart. |

